<p style="margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:24.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:break-word;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;word-spacing:0px;" bgcolor="white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">各个值解析</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">:</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">nowrap</span></strong><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;- </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">默认，</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">弹性容器为单行。该情况下弹性子项可能会溢出容器。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></li>
  <li><strong><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">wrap</span></strong><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;- </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">弹性容器为多行。该情况下弹性子项溢出的部分会被放置到新行，子项内部会发生断行</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></li>
  <li><strong><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">wrap-reverse</span></strong><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;-</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">反转</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> wrap </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">排列。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></li>
</ul>
