<h2 style="margin-top:1.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:1.5pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:21.6pt;background:white;" bgcolor="white"><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:21.5pt; color:#333333; ">align-content </span><span style="font-size:21.5pt; color:#333333; ">属性</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:21.5pt; color:#333333; "> </span></h2>
<p style="margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:24.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:break-word;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;word-spacing:0px;" bgcolor="white"><code><span style="color:#333333; ">align-content</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">属性用于修改</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;</span><code><span style="color:#333333; ">flex-wrap</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">属性的行为。类似于</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;</span><code><span style="color:#333333; ">align-items</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">, </span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">但它不是设置弹性子元素的对齐，而是设置各个行的对齐。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></p>
