<div style="border:solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt;border-left:solid #DDDDDD 3.0pt;padding:8.0pt 11.0pt 8.0pt 11.0pt;background:#FBFBFB;" bgcolor="#FBFBFB">
  <pre style="line-height:15.0pt;background:#FBFBFB;word-break:break-all;border:none;padding:0cm;border-image:initial;white-space:pre-wrap;overflow-wrap:break-word;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;background-position-x:50%;background-position-y:0%;word-spacing:0px;" bgcolor="#FBFBFB"><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; ">align</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">-</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; ">content</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">:</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; "> flex</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">-</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; ">start </span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">|</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; "> flex</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">-</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#000088; ">end</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; "> </span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">|</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; "> center </span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">|</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; "> space</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">-</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; ">between </span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">|</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; "> space</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">-</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; ">around </span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#666600; ">|</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:black; "> stretch</span><span style="font-family:Consolas; font-size:9.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></pre>
</div>
<p style="margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:24.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:break-word;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;word-spacing:0px;" bgcolor="white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">各个值解析</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">:</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><code><span style="border:none windowtext 1.0pt; padding:0cm; font-size:12.0pt; color:#333333; ">stretch</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;- </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">默认。各行将会伸展以占用剩余的空间。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></li>
  <li><code><span style="font-size:12.0pt; color:#333333; ">flex-start</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;- </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">各行向弹性盒容器的起始位置堆叠。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></li>
