  <li><code><span style="font-size:12.0pt; color:#333333; ">center</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;-</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">各行向弹性盒容器的中间位置堆叠。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></li>
  <li><code><span style="font-size:12.0pt; color:#333333; ">space-between</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;-</span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">各行在弹性盒容器中平均分布。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></li>
  <li><code><span style="font-size:12.0pt; color:#333333; ">space-around</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;- </span><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">各行在弹性盒容器中平均分布，两端保留子元素与子元素之间间距大小的一半。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></li>
</ul>
