<h3 style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:white;" bgcolor="white"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:17.0pt; color:#333333; ">对齐</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:17.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></h3>
<p style="margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:24.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:break-word;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;word-spacing:0px;" bgcolor="white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">设置</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&quot;margin&quot;</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">值为</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&quot;auto&quot;</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">值，自动获取弹性容器中剩余的空间。所以设置垂直方向</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">margin</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">值为</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&quot;auto&quot;</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">，可以使弹性子元素在弹性容器的两上轴方向都完全居中。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:24.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:break-word;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;word-spacing:0px;" bgcolor="white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">以下实例在第一个弹性子元素上设置了</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;</span><code><span style="color:#333333; ">margin-right:  auto;</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">。</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">它将剩余的空间放置在元素的右侧：</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<h3 style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0cm;background:white;" bgcolor="white"><span style="font-family:宋体; font-size:17.0pt; color:#333333; ">完美的居中</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:17.0pt; color:#333333; "> </span></h3>
