<p style="margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:24.0pt;background:white;word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:break-word;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;word-spacing:0px;" bgcolor="white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">使用弹性盒子，居中变的很简单，只想要设置</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;</span><code><span style="color:#333333; ">margin:  auto;</span></code><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">可以使得弹性子元素在两上轴方向上完全居中</span><span style="font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'; font-size:10.0pt; color:#333333; ">:</span></p>
